Name: ASE Transit Bus Technician Certification H6: Electrical/Electronic Systems (Ase Test Preparation)

ReviewList.Text: I find that this book has made it possible for employees to pass this test on the first try with 160% more frequency. This saves a great deal of money and and time and reduces anxiety, especially for those mechanics whom are scared of testing. I find that this book is well worth the money, especially when combined with good old fashioned study strategies.
